{"word":"G519 - ἀπάγχομαι - apánchomai - ap-ang'-khom-ahee - Hang himself","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπάγχομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apánchomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-ang'-khom-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Hang himself</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வேதனை"},{"paragraph":"anguish"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x0301;&#x03B3;&#x03C7;&#x03C9;</b> <b>agcho&#x0304;</b> (to <i>choke</i>; akin to the base of <a href=\"#/G43 - ἀγκάλη - ankálē - ang-kal'-ay/43\">G43</a>); to <i>strangle oneself off</i> (that is, to death): - hang himself.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}